<View className="leaderboard-container">
  <For source="{{tournamentPlayers}}" itemName="i">
        <View className="player-row">
          <!-- Row Frame Background -->
          <If>
            <Condition lhs="{{i.playerId}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="{{currentPlayerId}}" />
            <View><Image className="leader-bar-frame" src="leader_bar_green.png" /></View>
            <Else>
              <View><Image className="leader-bar-frame" src="leader_bar.png" /></View>
            </Else>
          </If>
          
          <!-- Rank with Background -->
          <View className="rank-container">
            <If>
              <Condition lhs="{{i.rank}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="1"/>
              <View><Image className="rank-background" src="../common/medal_gold.png" /></View>
            <ElseIf>
                <Condition lhs="{{i.rank}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="2" />
                <View><Image className="rank-background" src="../common/medal_silver.png" /></View>
            </ElseIf>
            <ElseIf>
                <Condition lhs="{{i.rank}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="3" />
                <View><Image className="rank-background" src="../common/medal_bronze.png" /></View>
              </ElseIf>
                <Else>
                  <View><Image className="rank-background" src="../common/bg_rank.png" /></View>
                </Else>
            </If>
            

            <Text className="rank-number" content="{{i.rank}}" />
          </View>
          
          <!-- Player Avatar -->
          <View className="avatar-container">
            <Image className="player-avatar" src="{{FBInstant.players[{{i.playerId}}].photo}}" />
          </View>
          
          <!-- Player Name -->
          <View className="name-container">
            <If>
              <Condition lhs="{{i.playerId}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="{{currentPlayerId}}" />
              <View><Text className="player-name-green" content="{{FBInstant.players[{{i.playerId}}].name}}" /></View>
              <Else>
                <View><Text className="player-name" content="{{FBInstant.players[{{i.playerId}}].name}}" /></View>
              </Else>
            </If>
          </View>
          
          <!-- Score with Background -->
          <View className="score-container">
            <Image className="score-background" src="../common/bg_score.png" />
            <Image className="cup-icon" src="../common/ico_cup.png" />
            <Text className="player-score" content="{{i.score}}" />
          </View>
        </View>
      </For>
</View>

<View className="invite-async-overlay">
  <Image src="invite-score.png" className="wideframe-invite-score"/>

</View>

<View className="tournament-container">
  <For source="{{tournamentPlayers}}" itemName="player">
    <If>
      <Condition lhs="{{player.rank}}" operator="NOT_GREATER_THAN" rhs="3"/>
      <If>
        <Condition lhs="{{player.rank}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="1"/>
        <View className="podium-position-1">
          <!-- Player Avatar -->
          <View className="avatar-section">
            <View className="avatar-container">
              <Image className="avatar-background" src="avatar_top.png" />
              <Image className="player-avatar" src="{{FBInstant.players[{{player.playerId}}].photo}}" />
            </View>
          </View>

          <!-- Rank Badge -->
          <View className="rank-badge-container-1">
            <View><Image className="rank-badge" src="../common/medal_gold.png" /></View>
            <Text className="rank-number-1" content="{{player.rank}}" />
          </View>
          
          <!-- Player Info -->
          <View className="player-info">
            <Text className="player-score" content="{{player.score}}" />
            <Text className="player-name" content="{{FBInstant.players[{{player.playerId}}].name}}" />
          </View>
        </View>
      <ElseIf>
        <Condition lhs="{{player.rank}}" operator="EQUALS" rhs="2"/>
        <View className="podium-position-2">
          <!-- Player Avatar -->
          <View className="avatar-section">
            <View className="avatar-container">
              <Image className="avatar-background" src="avatar_top.png" />
              <Image className="player-avatar" src="{{FBInstant.players[{{player.playerId}}].photo}}" />
            </View>
          </View>

          <!-- Rank Badge -->
          <View className="rank-badge-container">
            <View><Image className="rank-badge" src="../common/medal_silver.png" /></View>
            <Text className="rank-number-2" content="{{player.rank}}" />
          </View>
          
          <!-- Player Info -->
          <View className="player-info">
            <Text className="player-score" content="{{player.score}}" />
            <Text className="player-name" content="{{FBInstant.players[{{player.playerId}}].name}}" />
          </View>
        </View>
      </ElseIf>
      <Else>
        <View className="podium-position-3">
          <!-- Player Avatar -->
          <View className="avatar-section">
            <View className="avatar-container">
              <Image className="avatar-background" src="avatar_top.png" />
              <Image className="player-avatar" src="{{FBInstant.players[{{player.playerId}}].photo}}" />
            </View>
          </View>

          <!-- Rank Badge -->
          <View className="rank-badge-container">
            <View><Image className="rank-badge" src="../common/medal_bronze.png" /></View>
            <Text className="rank-number-3" content="{{player.rank}}" />
          </View>
          
          <!-- Player Info -->
          <View className="player-info">
            <Text className="player-score" content="{{player.score}}" />
            <Text className="player-name" content="{{FBInstant.players[{{player.playerId}}].name}}" />
          </View>
        </View>
      </Else>
      </If>
    </If>
  </For>
</View>
